    <item>
      <title>英国罢免反垄断监管机构主席以释放增长信号</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/uk-ousts-chair-of-antitrust-watchdog-to-send-growth-signal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府罢免了英国竞争监管机构竞争与市场管理局 (Competition and Markets Authority) 的主席，因为内阁大臣们试图强调他们希望监管机构采取更多措施促进经济增长的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/uk-ousts-chair-of-antitrust-watchdog-to-send-growth-signal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 19:57:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥称国务院不会“降级”至次要角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/rubio-says-state-won-t-be-relegated-to-secondary-role-anymore</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿马尔科·卢比奥在担任美国最高外交官后的首次讲话中承诺，确保他现在领导的机构在制定美国外交政策方面不会落后。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/rubio-says-state-won-t-be-relegated-to-secondary-role-anymore</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 19:55:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将与 OpenAI、软银、甲骨文合作，推动新一轮人工智能投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-to-announce-joint-openai-softbank-oracle-ai-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计美国总统唐纳德·特朗普将宣布一项由软银集团、OpenAI LLC 和甲骨文公司牵头的人工智能新投资计划，三家公司准备宣布成立一家价值数十亿美元的合资企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-to-announce-joint-openai-softbank-oracle-ai-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 18:13:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党主导的州就出生公民权计划起诉特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/democrat-led-states-sue-trump-over-birthright-citizenship-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党州检察长于周二对新政府发起了首次法庭斗争，起诉阻止唐纳德·特朗普总统终止在美国出生但父母非法入境或持非永久签证的孩子自动获得美国公民身份的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/democrat-led-states-sue-trump-over-birthright-citizenship-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 17:33:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多称特朗普的关税措施旨在制造混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-tariff-whiplash-is-designed-to-sow-chaos-trudeau-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普正试图在其贸易伙伴中制造不确定性，以使他们失去平衡并削弱他们的谈判地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-s-tariff-whiplash-is-designed-to-sow-chaos-trudeau-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 15:30:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
